{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "6d6d0109-a30f-4d26-85b5-1388bc5f8f8f", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/6d6d0109-a30f-4d26-85b5-1388bc5f8f8f@1.pkg/1772602522221/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602523159", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/6d6d0109-a30f-4d26-85b5-1388bc5f8f8f@1.pkg/1772602522221/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602523159"}, "identifier": "6d6d0109-a30f-4d26-85b5-1388bc5f8f8f", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>A尊君称对方的父亲敬称。B家君是对自己父亲的一种称呼。D“令郎”“令爱”是称呼对方儿子女儿</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>下列表述无误的一项是（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n", "title": "下列表述无误的一项是（    ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["C"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/6d6d0109-a30f-4d26-85b5-1388bc5f8f8f@1.pkg/item.json?v=1751721249394", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>“尊君”是谦词，是对自己父亲的一种称呼。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>君是对对方的敬称，家君是对人称对方的父亲，谦词。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>“与儿女讲论文义”一句中“儿女”是指公（谢安）兄长的儿子和女儿。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<p>公（谢安）可以称“胡儿”“无奕女”为“令郎”“令爱”。</p>\n"}], "prompt": "<p>下列表述无误的一项是（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "5136342961", "5036342749", "$RE0200", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bebf7c-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "5136342961", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bebf7c-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "6d6d0109-a30f-4d26-85b5-1388bc5f8f8f", "global_title": {"zh-CN": "下列表述无误的一项是（    ）"}, "global_description": {"zh-CN": "<p>下列表述无误的一项是（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n"}, "global_keywords": {}, "global_label": {}, "custom_properties": {"sys_packing_status": "ready", "preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/6d6d0109-a30f-4d26-85b5-1388bc5f8f8f@1.pkg/1772602522221/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602523159", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/6d6d0109-a30f-4d26-85b5-1388bc5f8f8f@1.pkg/1772602522221/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602523159"}, "auto_fill_thumb": true, "prom_